A little repo for keeping my vim configuration across all my machines.

Make sure you have Pathogen installed before installation.

Installation:
    git clone git://github.com/hzach/dotfiles.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
